OL,3,CScotland's relationship with Union at
OL,4,Cstake as vote counting begins
OL,6,FScotland's relationship with the Union
OL,7,Fis at stake as counting begins in the
OL,8,Fnation.
OL,10,FThe SNP is hoping to win another
OL,11,Fhistoric majority at Holyrood, and if
OL,12,Fthey do, they say Independence will be
OL,13,Ftop of their agenda.
OL,15,FThey haven't won that 65-seat majority
OL,16,Fsince 2011, under Alex Salmond.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
