OL,3,CScotland's relationship with Union at
OL,4,Cstake as vote counting begins
OL,6,FThe rise of Reform could split the
OL,7,Funionist vote between Labour, the
OL,8,FScottish Conservatives and Scottish
OL,9,FLiberal Democrats that wants to keep
OL,10,Fthe SNP out.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FReform UK Scotland is expected to
OL,18,Fperform well on the regional list
OL,19,Fvote, rather than the constituency
OL,20,Fvotes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
