OL,3,CScotland's relationship with Union at
OL,4,Cstake as vote counting begins
OL,6,FIt will also be all eyes on how
OL,7,FScottish Labour fares and whether
OL,8,FLabour's perceived poor performance in
OL,9,FWestminster has impacted their chances
OL,10,Fin Scotland.
OL,12,FScottish leader Anas Sarwar will also
OL,13,Fface some tough questions if his party
OL,14,Fperform badly in Scotland.
OL,16,FHe publicly called for Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer to resign over his decision to
OL,18,Fappoint Peter Mandelson as US
OL,19,FAmbassador.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
