OL,3,CScotland's relationship with Union at
OL,4,Cstake as vote counting begins
OL,6,FDuring the campaign, John Swinney said
OL,7,Fhe will seek to have another Scottish
OL,8,FIndependence Referendum by 2028.
OL,10,FThe Scottish Green co-leaders, Ross
OL,11,FGreer and Gilian Mackay said they will
OL,12,Fsupport the SNP to have a pro-
OL,13,Findependence majority at Holyrood.
OL,15,FIn the 2024 general election, the SNP
OL,16,Flost all six Glasgow seats to Labour.
OL,17,FA hammer blow for the party there.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
